    "id": "RR23UmbrellaMeasure",
    "text": {
        "status": "extensions",
        "div": "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><h1>Roadrunners Syndrome - Umbrella measure</h1><h2>Purpose</h2>As a preventive measure, supply those that suffered from a rockfall injury with a tiny ACME umbrella.<h2>Measure details</h2>Proportional measure, returns the proportion of patients (over the agen of 16) who suffered a rock fall injury and who where supplied with a tiny ACME umbrella within 7 days of the recording of the incident.</div>"
    },
